# General Project Rules

## Framework & Language

- Follow Nuxt 3 conventions and best practices
- Use TypeScript for type safety
- Prefer composables over plugins when possible
- Maintain consistency with existing code patterns

## Development Practices

- **Always check Nuxt UI for components before creating custom ones** - Use the Nuxt UI MCP server to search for existing components that match your needs before implementing custom components
- Check documentation before implementing similar functionality
- Follow existing code patterns and conventions
- Ensure type safety with TypeScript
- Use proper error handling patterns
